---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 404 — Page introuvable
permalink: /404.html
description: La page que vous cherchez n'existe pas.
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

{% set extraCss %}
.nf-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 6rem 1.5rem; min-height: 60vh; text-align: center; }
.nf-code { font-size: 7rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1; color: var(--red); letter-spacing: -0.05em; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
.nf-title { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
.nf-text { font-size: 1rem; color: #aaa; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 480px; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
.nf-links { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
.nf-links a { color: var(--power); text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid var(--accent); padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s; }
.nf-links a:hover { border-color: var(--power); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
@media (max-width: 600px) { .nf-code { font-size: 5rem; } .nf-title { font-size: 1.4rem; } }
{% endset %}

{% block content %}
<div class="nf-wrap">
    <div class="nf-code">404</div>
    <h1 class="nf-title">Page introuvable</h1>
    <p class="nf-text">La page que vous cherchez a été déplacée, supprimée, ou n'a jamais existé. Aucune carte ne mène ici.</p>
    <div class="nf-links">
        <a href="/">Retour à l'accueil</a>
        <a href="/latest/">Derniers articles</a>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
